Meet Tinted Windows, a super group consisting of Taylor Hanson (Hanson), James Iha (Smashing Pumpkins), Adam Schlesinger (FOW), and Bun E Carlos (Cheap Trick). They fuse the sounds of power-pop, rock and New Wave of the late 70's and early 80's with the more modern rock and pop sounds of their own groups. The result is a fun,stripped-down, high energy record.
